reviewText: This is probably no doubt the wrong media to post this response but I cannot make a true response to the DVD because the provider still has not sent the product!!! I Love the artist but the supplier is the "pits" so until I receive my order I cannot make a legitimate remark or rating!!! Thank you, Leonard Harris

I love this DVD. It is just great and no one should miss it.
Kurt come back to Germany! It is a pleasure to listen to your music
Excellent Timing on the S&H!!!! It Holds perfectly and has great tension in the spring and doesn't bear down on the neck and frets of the guitar....EXCELLENT PRODUCT!!!!
Another uplifting classic! Kurt Carr is an awesome worshipper. I love this DVD and the songs are uplifting. God has really blessed this man.
